  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Check</title>

    <para>Installez <application>Check</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Pour tester l'installation, lancez <userinput>make check</userinput>.</para>

    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make docdir=/usr/share/doc/check-&check-version; install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

